{"type": "article", "id": 46832, "title": "旺仔翻拍经典广告，Dolce&Gabbana推出限量版意面 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-11-03T04:34:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 929, "name": "乐高"}, {"id": 1520, "name": "Uber"}, {"id": 27971, "name": "旺仔"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 25, "praise_count": 118, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171103114235i275Yu1Np46LIlT9.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #aaaaaa} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #aaaaaa; min-height: 14.0px} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #aaaaaa} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 22.0px} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; color: #323333; min-height: 14.0px} p.p9 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px Times; min-height: 14.0px} p.p10 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 10.0px 0.0px; line-height: 23.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939} p.p11 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; color: #393939; min-height: 19.0px} p.p12 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 12.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #aaaaaa; -webkit-text-stroke: #aaaaaa; min-height: 14.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 14.0px 'Microsoft YaHei'; font-kerning: none; color: #393939} span.s3 {font: 12.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #323333} span.s5 {font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 14.0px Arial; font-kerning: none} span.s7 {font: 14.0px 'Heiti SC Light'; font-kerning: none; color: #323333} span.s8 {font: 12.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>明星又代言了啥</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/02/ladygaga-stars-in-tudors-borntodare-campaign-20171102/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>瑞士腕表品牌帝舵（Tudor）发布广告大片，由新晋品牌大使 LADY GAGA 出演</b></a>，诠释品牌宣言“天生敢为”，可以说是非常合题了。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103114438a1OE5PjsiYXD2F4e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.503175\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=h0568d717dy&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-11-02/dolce-gabbana-is-now-in-the-pasta-business\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Dolce &amp; Gabbana 和意大利意面商 Pastificio di Martino 合作推出限量版意面和围裙，11 月 15 日在全球发行 5000 套装盒，售价 110 美元</b></a>。Pastificio di Martino 拥有 100 多年品牌历史，现在年营收额能达到 1.63 亿美元。2018 巴黎时装周春季秀场上 Dolce &amp; Gabbana 的食物主题服装也不少。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711031211159T1ULwJWOluF56hs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103121202qKfUcemTXGp3Ju0n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103121211YKk8jw3poJdNSv6R.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.260606\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42577\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>三得利找范冰冰、张震、孙俪、乐基儿拍了个广告合集</b></a>，情节很简单，就是拍他们吃拉面、吃咖喱、吃小笼包、喝乌龙茶的过程，吃得还挺好看的。掌镜的是有“日本广告摄影界大师”之称的上田义彦。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103114622xUQO27Rlk0g3rIDB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103114652qD7cbFn2m6WuLQx0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.655000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103114659DwOlec2u40ICPWsB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=r05666lecvr&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/42570\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>飞猪发布了首支品牌视频</b></a>，拍了四个改编自真实体验的旅行故事。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=y0564vrffch&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23821.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>银行广告越来越爱讲故事，麦肯上海给交通银行拍了三支短片</b></a>。分别讲了猫咪救助人、拍摄抗战老兵的摄影师和小学地理老师的故事，表达“有意义的想法，值得全情兑现”的广告主题，为的是推销交通银行信用卡的贷款新品“好现贷”。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=z05687y9fiz&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t<figcaption class=\"\"><b>《玛莎的猫舍》</b></figcaption></figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/23801.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雅马哈结合自身 logo 中的弧线元素，拍了一支“微笑弧线”品牌宣传片，</b></a>挑选了十余个场景，用弧线来演绎生活。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103115225K4twERiSamdYlbLs.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.465625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=l0561m2wnnr&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/02/though-you-are-a-parent-you-behave-like-a-child-facing-with-the-things-you-favor/\" rel=\"nofollow\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><b>雷克萨斯（Lexus）最新的广告创意</b></a>，说挚爱的东西往往会激发成年人“内在的童真”，看到自己喜欢的车（雷克萨斯汽车），成年人就会像小孩子一样欣喜若狂，分别拍了男生、女生两个版本。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=x056848t4x3&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAwNDM3MTUyMw==&amp;mid=2649852116&amp;idx=2&amp;sn=831ddab309317e10ff1f694515e6272a&amp;chksm=8329cdf8b45e44ee891995115e16b0b42f22380edc57b544e342e66f5e5d39b374149d8ff0ad&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1102Etp8ni886w2K5iVzYTod&amp;key=0fe6c5d8c1ba2581bb70674214959adb8739103ef737670d3bc7dfce57faa74aa04edde5424ee87e716441a35ed6b0a931ffbf1653e8b918dd19422879011f75817fcad4e5f5c16dc16250db651fc8f1&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;pass_ticket=kV%2BmXt%2Fofw7ZeYSWLKQBdiqbw34DaBPT%2F4DSDWQ8OQaqZHF%2ByRX30VIBw3iRBQGg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>童年的旺仔牛奶洗脑广告有了续集，长大后成为小学教师的李子明再次迎来了给他送大桶旺仔牛奶的母亲（据说找的演员和小时候是同一个人）</b></a>。这是旺旺为双十一拍摄的搞怪广告，打情怀牌配合这次长大成人的主题，双十一旺旺还会在天猫上出售放大版的旺旺仙贝和雪饼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103120350r0MCpejoOSqz9Pl7.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.074010\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=k05684oqwgb&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://www.creativereview.co.uk/airbnb-offers-opportunity-stay-night-lego-house/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Airbnb 和乐高合作，在丹麦比隆推出了新的奇屋一夜活动“乐高之家”</b></a>，在占地 1.2 万平方米的乐高店里玩积木，然后在 2,500 万块乐高积木的包围下进入梦乡。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><i></i><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103120819g5KuykZjFvCs068U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201711031208394E9ma8T7njbc5fHV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171103120857jpOgH7xPrvVMmW4t.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.672767\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>最后，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/02/amazon-consolidates-its-1-billion-plus-global-media-buying-business-with-ipg-mediabrands/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>历时三个月的媒介业务比稿，亚马逊宣布 IPG 盟博赢得了这项价值 10 亿美元的全球媒介业务。</b></a>据凯度媒体数据，亚马逊在 2016 年美国受测量媒体上的花费为 9.5 亿美元，这个数字在过去四年中翻了一番。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/11/02/uber-launches-its-first-global-creative-review-and-begins-talks-with-media-agencies/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Uber 首次发起全球创意业务比稿，寻找全球创意代理合作伙伴</b></a>。Uber 目前面临着越来越激烈的市场竞争，其竞争对手 Lyft 于今年早些时候委任 W+K纽约、DigitasLBi 旧金山为其创意代理商和数字媒介代理商。<br></p><p>来自 Kantar Media 的数据显示，2016 年优步在美国市场内部可测量媒介上花费了约 7200 万美元，其全球营销费用具体数字尚未可知。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2017/11/01/facebook-earnings-q3-2017.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Facebook 第三财季利润提升 79%，其中广告销售额达到 101 亿美元，有 89 亿美元来自移动广告收入，占 88%</b></a>。截至 9 月 30 日，Facebook 称平台上超过 600 万广告客户正把更多预算投向移动端的用户。<br></p><p class=\"\">CFO David Wehner 指出，未来广告价格对广告收入的影响要比销售的广告数量更重要，这是在暗示 Facebook 的视频广告战略正在取得进展。扎克伯格表示，到明年年底，公司会有 2 万名致力于打击假新闻和仇恨言论的工作人员，这会推高运营成本。</p><p class=\"\">题图来源：旺旺</p>"}